	   <tr><td colspan=2>Try camping the rockhoppers in Downshround Peaks.<br><br>Make sure you have sow, the hoppers are pretty quick. Cast Vocerate Earth and guard him about 50 feet from the hopper cave. Don't pull with Malise, just a waste of mana.&nbsp;&nbsp;Just get close enough to the hopper to aggro you.  Pull hopper back. Send pet into attack and med. Wait until pet is about 25% health than start casting new pet.  Right before the cast time is done , do a /pet get lost.  Send new pet in, and when the hopper has a sliver of health left, do /pet get lost.  Than nuke with one of you lower nukes ( I use Blaze). Mob is dead, full xp, and my mana is full.  It usually takes 2 earth pets to kill hoppers (sometimes one), so bring plenty of malachites. No down time and great xp!  I am getting 2 blues pet hour. The loot sucks on the hoppers unless you are a tailor.  I am going to finish level through 52, and I bet 53 will continue to be good xp.<br><br>(ie chain casting pets)<br><br>Hope this info helps<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Errain Gemmaster, 53rd Season Magician</td></tr>
