	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hmm... there is a good quest in qeynos for +3 int earrings. I dont know what your faction will be, but if you hunt gnolls for a bit you can get it up(good exp in blackburrow anyway, also you could hand in gnoll teeth for faction if your dubious. Just hail the guy standing by the entrance to the aquaducts by&nbsp;&nbsp;the bank. He will tell you something abotu a dress. Go down and kill anything that moves look for a named cube Cubert. kill him a few times get the tattered dress or whatever and hand it in. Takes a few times but eventually you'll get +3 int earrings. (You might wanna look up the quest here and check out the info, im not positive that is all accurate except it taking a few tries and you kill cubert for the dress or whatever)<br><br>Good luck!<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
