	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f101794095066583><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=12&mid=101794095066583>Burning Embers</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=12&mid=101794095066583#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=97366><span id= >Errain</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>23 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Thu, Apr 4th 12:26 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[1.75]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I hunted BW last night for the burning embers. Here are my finds.<br><br>1. We camped for about 4 1/2 hours and had 6 named wurms spawn ( 4 Nez and 2 Phur).<br><br>2. We camped at the -450, -2550 loc.<br><br>3. Group consisted of 2 mages (51 and 52), 45 enchanter, 51 bard, 54 rogue, and 53 druid. Without cleric, fear kiting was the only way to go. This group handled the area pretty well.<br><br>4. Named wurms do gravity flux, so levition is recommended during fight.<br><br>5. Drops: 4 wurm guts (2 happy bards and 2 rotted), 1 wurm coat, but no embers.<br><br>6. The named wurms and their PH's are on a 90 second timer. Once you find and kill the PH, the camp is cake, just set up camp at the -450, -2550 loc. If you dont kill the PH, it will head east.<br><br>7. When we arrived at camp, Nez was up. Had trouble taking him down, due to new group working together. We had down time due to one death, so we lost PH. We spent the next hour and half killing everything, then, Phur finally spawned. The next 2 out of 3 spawns were the named. We spent another hour or so killing the PH's and Nez spawned back to back. So, it seems that the named will spawn in flurrys, followed by a lot of PH's.<br><br>8. I hope this helps!!<br><br>Please look me up. I am planning to put together groups every night until I get the embers.<br><br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Errain Gemmaster, 53rd Season Magician</td></tr>
