	   <tr><td colspan=2>Errain is partially wrong. I don't know the situation on his server but high level mages on my server are in great demand. Due to some of their very handy spells such as summon hero. Although if you are going to start out for a first character you have to take into consideration this fact. Are you going to take this guy past level 20? I personally don't reccomend casters for a first character unless you know how to make plat fairly fast. Or if you have some friends who can help you out. On the other hand, if you want a nice challenge to start out go with a caster. Enchanters are nice but wizards can port and that gives you a bit of an upperhand in traveling for leveling. Of course its always hard to solo while mages have a natural soloing skills. What ever you decide good luck!<br>&nbsp;<br>The time will come when proof of the real one shall come. In those days I will carry out his will. Until then I shall prove the falsehood of these measly worthless false&nbsp;&nbsp;gods.<br>Chupon</td></tr>
